=Description=

Matthew Cropp:

"For the most part they are consumer co-ops, though black star has some interesting worker self-management. The strategic importance is the creation of community-controlled third places as an alternative to extractive ownership in the craft beer space. The peer support Facebook group is Co-op brewery group."

